## API (Axum, porta 5555)

- **Takeout**: GET `/health`, GET `/pair/info`, POST `/pair/renew`, POST `/pair`, GET `/participants/search?q=...&mode=...`, GET `/participants/:id`, POST `/takeout/confirm`, GET `/audit`, POST `/admin/import`. POST `/takeout/confirm` usa `request_id` (UUID) para idempotĂŞncia. Respostas JSON; HTTP 200, 400, 401, 404, 422.
- **Sync (somente com internet)**: GET `/sync/pull?eventId=`, POST `/sync/push` â€” proxy para a plataforma de ticket (thevent); 503 quando sem conectividade. Base URL thevent: `THEVENT_BASE_URL`.

